cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SI 

This paper is about neural network learning and backpropagation, which are core topics in machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also discusses the theoretical characteristics of the proposed framework, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). Additionally, the experiments involve image classification, which could be categorized under cs.CV (Computer Vision).
